:: Dawn Approach White [dawn-approach dawn-approach-white piano-bed] {"position":"1850,150","size":"100,100"}
<script>/* Fallback for the iframe-ready class. The iframe's own onload sets it after 400ms — but if the iframe is very slow or fails to load entirely, lightning would never fire (it's CSS-gated on .iframe-ready). 4s fallback ensures the bolts play even in degraded-network / WebGL-down scenarios. In the common case (HTTP-prefetched iframe loads in <1s) the onload handler wins and the fallback no-ops. */setTimeout(function(){var d=document.querySelector('.dawn-approach');if(d&&!d.classList.contains('iframe-ready'))d.classList.add('iframe-ready');},4000);</script>\
