(if: $seenCoachPipe is false)[(set: $seenCoachPipe to true)<script>setTimeout(function(){ if (window.dssAudio && window.dssAudio.cosmicSewerSuck) window.dssAudio.cosmicSewerSuck(); }, 40);</script>
<div class="coach-plumbing-intro" aria-hidden="true">
<svg viewBox="-100 -100 200 200" preserveAspectRatio="xMidYMid meet"><defs><radialGradient id="cpiPipe" cx="50%" cy="50%" r="50%"><stop offset="0%"  stop-color="rgba(40,28,14,0.0)"/><stop offset="38%" stop-color="rgba(22,16,8,0.55)"/><stop offset="72%" stop-color="rgba(10,7,3,0.92)"/><stop offset="100%" stop-color="rgba(4,3,1,1)"/></radialGradient><radialGradient id="cpiCore" cx="50%" cy="50%" r="50%"><stop offset="0%"   stop-color="rgba(220,168,86,0.95)"/><stop offset="45%"  stop-color="rgba(160,112,48,0.7)"/><stop offset="100%" stop-color="rgba(80,52,20,0)"/></radialGradient><radialGradient id="cpiPorcelain" cx="50%" cy="42%" r="55%"><stop offset="0%"  stop-color="rgba(220,205,180,0.85)"/><stop offset="55%" stop-color="rgba(180,160,128,0.7)"/><stop offset="92%" stop-color="rgba(120,98,70,0.4)"/><stop offset="100%" stop-color="rgba(60,46,28,0)"/></radialGradient><radialGradient id="cpiVortexFill" cx="50%" cy="50%" r="50%"><stop offset="0%"   stop-color="rgba(98,86,40,0.7)"/><stop offset="45%"  stop-color="rgba(76,64,32,0.65)"/><stop offset="85%"  stop-color="rgba(46,38,18,0.4)"/><stop offset="100%" stop-color="rgba(20,16,8,0)"/></radialGradient><linearGradient id="cpiRust"   x1="0" x2="1"><stop offset="0%" stop-color="rgba(186,108,52,0)"/><stop offset="50%" stop-color="rgba(212,128,60,1)"/><stop offset="100%" stop-color="rgba(186,108,52,0)"/></linearGradient><linearGradient id="cpiSepia"  x1="0" x2="1"><stop offset="0%" stop-color="rgba(160,124,72,0)"/><stop offset="50%" stop-color="rgba(196,150,86,1)"/><stop offset="100%" stop-color="rgba(160,124,72,0)"/></linearGradient><linearGradient id="cpiBrass"  x1="0" x2="1"><stop offset="0%" stop-color="rgba(168,140,72,0)"/><stop offset="50%" stop-color="rgba(204,168,86,1)"/><stop offset="100%" stop-color="rgba(168,140,72,0)"/></linearGradient><linearGradient id="cpiSlime"  x1="0" x2="1"><stop offset="0%" stop-color="rgba(108,124,68,0)"/><stop offset="50%" stop-color="rgba(146,166,88,1)"/><stop offset="100%" stop-color="rgba(108,124,68,0)"/></linearGradient><linearGradient id="cpiAlgae"  x1="0" x2="1"><stop offset="0%" stop-color="rgba(78,96,56,0)"/><stop offset="50%" stop-color="rgba(110,134,72,1)"/><stop offset="100%" stop-color="rgba(78,96,56,0)"/></linearGradient><linearGradient id="cpiCopper" x1="0" x2="1"><stop offset="0%" stop-color="rgba(140,90,52,0)"/><stop offset="50%" stop-color="rgba(176,116,68,1)"/><stop offset="100%" stop-color="rgba(140,90,52,0)"/></linearGradient><linearGradient id="cpiOlive"  x1="0" x2="1"><stop offset="0%" stop-color="rgba(96,86,40,0)"/><stop offset="50%" stop-color="rgba(132,116,52,1)"/><stop offset="100%" stop-color="rgba(96,86,40,0)"/></linearGradient><linearGradient id="cpiMurk"   x1="0" x2="1"><stop offset="0%" stop-color="rgba(80,62,38,0)"/><stop offset="50%" stop-color="rgba(110,86,50,1)"/><stop offset="100%" stop-color="rgba(80,62,38,0)"/></linearGradient><filter id="cpiGlow" x="-50%" y="-50%" width="200%" height="200%"><feGaussianBlur stdDeviation="2.2" result="b1"/><feGaussianBlur stdDeviation="5" result="b2"/><feMerge><feMergeNode in="b2"/><feMergeNode in="b1"/><feMergeNode in="SourceGraphic"/></feMerge></filter><filter id="cpiSoft" x="-50%" y="-50%" width="200%" height="200%"><feGaussianBlur stdDeviation="1.6"/></filter><!-- Grime texture: turbulent noise to make the pipe wall feel encrusted --><filter id="cpiGrime" x="-50%" y="-50%" width="200%" height="200%"><feTurbulence baseFrequency="0.85" numOctaves="3" seed="7" result="noise"/><feColorMatrix in="noise" type="matrix" values="0 0 0 0 0.30  0 0 0 0 0.22  0 0 0 0 0.10  0 0 0 0.55 0"/></filter></defs>
<!-- Pipe-shaft blackness — heavy, no light reaches here -->
<rect x="-100" y="-100" width="200" height="200" fill="rgba(4,3,1,1)"/>
<!-- Encrusted grimy wall texture filling the periphery -->
<rect x="-100" y="-100" width="200" height="200" fill="rgba(60,42,20,0.55)" filter="url(#cpiGrime)" opacity="0.9"/>
<!-- Pipe-throat vignette — dark heart, dirty amber periphery -->
<circle cx="0" cy="0" r="100" fill="url(#cpiPipe)" opacity="0.95"/>
<!-- Stagnant brown-green sewer water pooled at the bottom of the pipe.
     Translucent so the dark pipe shows through; the surface sloshes
     side to side, the meniscus tilts, so the pool reads as restless. -->
<g class="cpi-water" opacity="0.58">
  <defs>
    <linearGradient id="cpiWaterFill" x1="0" y1="0" x2="0" y2="1">
      <stop offset="0%"   stop-color="rgba(76,82,42,0.45)"/>
      <stop offset="30%"  stop-color="rgba(56,60,28,0.55)"/>
      <stop offset="100%" stop-color="rgba(30,32,12,0.7)"/>
    </linearGradient>
    <linearGradient id="cpiWaterSheen" x1="0" x2="1">
      <stop offset="0%"   stop-color="rgba(150,158,98,0)"/>
      <stop offset="40%"  stop-color="rgba(176,186,118,0.7)"/>
      <stop offset="60%"  stop-color="rgba(176,186,118,0.7)"/>
      <stop offset="100%" stop-color="rgba(150,158,98,0)"/>
    </linearGradient>
  </defs>
  <!-- Water body — wavy top edge, fills the bottom of the viewBox -->
  <path class="cpi-water-body" d="M -100,48 Q -75,40 -50,46 Q -25,52 0,44 Q 25,38 50,46 Q 75,52 100,42 L 100,100 L -100,100 Z" fill="url(#cpiWaterFill)"/>
  <!-- Meniscus highlight — bright skin on the surface -->
  <path class="cpi-water-sheen" d="M -100,48 Q -75,40 -50,46 Q -25,52 0,44 Q 25,38 50,46 Q 75,52 100,42" fill="none" stroke="url(#cpiWaterSheen)" stroke-width="0.6" opacity="0.85"/>
  <!-- A few scum patches floating on the surface -->
  <ellipse cx="-40" cy="50" rx="14" ry="1.4" fill="rgba(96,108,52,0.55)"/>
  <ellipse cx="22"  cy="46" rx="10" ry="1.2" fill="rgba(88,100,48,0.5)"/>
  <ellipse cx="62"  cy="48" rx="8"  ry="1.0" fill="rgba(108,118,60,0.5)"/>
  <!-- Surface bubbles — the kind you don't want to think about -->
  <circle cx="-58" cy="49" r="1.4" fill="rgba(180,178,120,0.55)"/>
  <circle cx="-18" cy="47" r="0.9" fill="rgba(170,168,110,0.45)"/>
  <circle cx="44"  cy="45" r="1.2" fill="rgba(190,184,128,0.5)"/>
  <circle cx="78"  cy="48" r="0.8" fill="rgba(176,170,116,0.45)"/>
</g>
<!-- Forward-motion streaks: bright dashes that elongate radially as we
     accelerate down the pipe. Each streak rides its own keyframe; the
     staggered delays make a chain of velocity-trails always on screen. -->
<g class="cpi-streaks" filter="url(#cpiGlow)" opacity="0.9">
  <line class="cpi-streak cpi-streak-1"  x1="0" y1="0" x2="0"   y2="-100" stroke="rgba(220,180,110,0.85)" stroke-width="0.7" stroke-linecap="round"/>
  <line class="cpi-streak cpi-streak-2"  x1="0" y1="0" x2="71"  y2="-71"  stroke="rgba(208,160,90,0.85)"  stroke-width="0.7" stroke-linecap="round"/>
  <line class="cpi-streak cpi-streak-3"  x1="0" y1="0" x2="100" y2="0"    stroke="rgba(190,148,82,0.85)"  stroke-width="0.7" stroke-linecap="round"/>
  <line class="cpi-streak cpi-streak-4"  x1="0" y1="0" x2="71"  y2="71"   stroke="rgba(180,140,76,0.85)"  stroke-width="0.7" stroke-linecap="round"/>
  <line class="cpi-streak cpi-streak-5"  x1="0" y1="0" x2="0"   y2="100"  stroke="rgba(170,130,72,0.85)"  stroke-width="0.7" stroke-linecap="round"/>
  <line class="cpi-streak cpi-streak-6"  x1="0" y1="0" x2="-71" y2="71"   stroke="rgba(160,124,66,0.85)"  stroke-width="0.7" stroke-linecap="round"/>
  <line class="cpi-streak cpi-streak-7"  x1="0" y1="0" x2="-100" y2="0"   stroke="rgba(168,128,70,0.85)"  stroke-width="0.7" stroke-linecap="round"/>
  <line class="cpi-streak cpi-streak-8"  x1="0" y1="0" x2="-71" y2="-71"  stroke="rgba(200,150,80,0.85)"  stroke-width="0.7" stroke-linecap="round"/>
  <line class="cpi-streak cpi-streak-9"  x1="0" y1="0" x2="38"  y2="-92"  stroke="rgba(140,110,60,0.7)"   stroke-width="0.55" stroke-linecap="round"/>
  <line class="cpi-streak cpi-streak-10" x1="0" y1="0" x2="92"  y2="-38"  stroke="rgba(140,110,60,0.7)"   stroke-width="0.55" stroke-linecap="round"/>
  <line class="cpi-streak cpi-streak-11" x1="0" y1="0" x2="92"  y2="38"   stroke="rgba(140,110,60,0.7)"   stroke-width="0.55" stroke-linecap="round"/>
  <line class="cpi-streak cpi-streak-12" x1="0" y1="0" x2="38"  y2="92"   stroke="rgba(140,110,60,0.7)"   stroke-width="0.55" stroke-linecap="round"/>
  <line class="cpi-streak cpi-streak-13" x1="0" y1="0" x2="-38" y2="92"   stroke="rgba(140,110,60,0.7)"   stroke-width="0.55" stroke-linecap="round"/>
  <line class="cpi-streak cpi-streak-14" x1="0" y1="0" x2="-92" y2="38"   stroke="rgba(140,110,60,0.7)"   stroke-width="0.55" stroke-linecap="round"/>
  <line class="cpi-streak cpi-streak-15" x1="0" y1="0" x2="-92" y2="-38"  stroke="rgba(140,110,60,0.7)"   stroke-width="0.55" stroke-linecap="round"/>
  <line class="cpi-streak cpi-streak-16" x1="0" y1="0" x2="-38" y2="-92"  stroke="rgba(140,110,60,0.7)"   stroke-width="0.55" stroke-linecap="round"/>
</g>
<!-- Receding pipe rings — every ring is a rust/brass/slime band. They
     are born tiny at the focal point and rocket outward; the staggered
     starts plus iterating loops produce a constant chain rushing toward
     the camera. -->
<g class="cpi-tunnel" filter="url(#cpiGlow)">
  <circle class="cpi-ring cpi-ring-1"  cx="0" cy="0" r="6" fill="none" stroke="#D4843C" stroke-width="2.2"/>
  <circle class="cpi-ring cpi-ring-2"  cx="0" cy="0" r="6" fill="none" stroke="#C49656" stroke-width="2.2"/>
  <circle class="cpi-ring cpi-ring-3"  cx="0" cy="0" r="6" fill="none" stroke="#CCA856" stroke-width="2.2"/>
  <circle class="cpi-ring cpi-ring-4"  cx="0" cy="0" r="6" fill="none" stroke="#92A658" stroke-width="2.2"/>
  <circle class="cpi-ring cpi-ring-5"  cx="0" cy="0" r="6" fill="none" stroke="#6E8648" stroke-width="2.2"/>
  <circle class="cpi-ring cpi-ring-6"  cx="0" cy="0" r="6" fill="none" stroke="#B07444" stroke-width="2.2"/>
  <circle class="cpi-ring cpi-ring-7"  cx="0" cy="0" r="6" fill="none" stroke="#846E36" stroke-width="2.2"/>
  <circle class="cpi-ring cpi-ring-8"  cx="0" cy="0" r="6" fill="none" stroke="#D4843C" stroke-width="2.2"/>
  <circle class="cpi-ring cpi-ring-9"  cx="0" cy="0" r="6" fill="none" stroke="#CCA856" stroke-width="2.2"/>
  <circle class="cpi-ring cpi-ring-10" cx="0" cy="0" r="6" fill="none" stroke="#92A658" stroke-width="2.2"/>
  <circle class="cpi-ring cpi-ring-11" cx="0" cy="0" r="6" fill="none" stroke="#B07444" stroke-width="2.2"/>
  <circle class="cpi-ring cpi-ring-12" cx="0" cy="0" r="6" fill="none" stroke="#846E36" stroke-width="2.2"/>
</g>
<!-- Bubbles rising out of the murk: small irregular circles trail past
     the camera, reinforcing the "we are submerged and ascending" read. -->
<g class="cpi-bubbles" opacity="0.85" filter="url(#cpiSoft)">
  <circle class="cpi-bubble cpi-bubble-1" cx="-22" cy="0" r="2.2" fill="rgba(196,178,128,0.7)"/>
  <circle class="cpi-bubble cpi-bubble-2" cx="14"  cy="0" r="1.6" fill="rgba(176,156,108,0.7)"/>
  <circle class="cpi-bubble cpi-bubble-3" cx="32"  cy="0" r="2.8" fill="rgba(208,184,132,0.65)"/>
  <circle class="cpi-bubble cpi-bubble-4" cx="-44" cy="0" r="1.9" fill="rgba(166,144,96,0.7)"/>
  <circle class="cpi-bubble cpi-bubble-5" cx="6"   cy="0" r="3.0" fill="rgba(214,190,140,0.7)"/>
  <circle class="cpi-bubble cpi-bubble-6" cx="-12" cy="0" r="1.4" fill="rgba(192,168,118,0.7)"/>
</g>
<!-- Focal-point at the end of the pipe — starts small and grimy-amber
     like a far bulb, ends as a SOLID bright disc filling the screen: the
     literal end of the pipe, the porcelain mouth you arrive at. Two
     layers: an outer halo that glows and grows, and an inner solid disc
     that remains a hard-edged circle even as it consumes the viewport. -->
<g class="cpi-focal">
  <g filter="url(#cpiGlow)">
    <circle cx="0" cy="0" r="26" fill="url(#cpiCore)"/>
    <circle cx="0" cy="0" r="10" fill="rgba(232,182,98,0.92)"/>
  </g>
  <circle class="cpi-focal-disc" cx="0" cy="0" r="3.6" fill="rgba(252,230,180,1)"/>
</g>
<!-- Trippy rotating arms — pastel rainbow petals nesting inward. Each
     arm is a different colour; the whole group spins as one. -->
<g class="cpi-arms" filter="url(#cpiGlow)"><path d="M 0,-92 C 36,-74 66,-42 82,0 C 66,42 36,74 0,92 C -36,74 -66,42 -82,0 C -66,-42 -36,-74 0,-92 Z" fill="none" stroke="url(#cpiPink)" stroke-width="2.2" opacity="0.95"/><path d="M 0,-78 C 30,-62 56,-32 68,0 C 56,32 30,62 0,78 C -30,62 -56,32 -68,0 C -56,-32 -30,-62 0,-78 Z" fill="none" stroke="url(#cpiPeach)" stroke-width="2.0" opacity="0.92"/><path d="M 0,-64 C 24,-50 46,-24 56,0 C 46,24 24,50 0,64 C -24,50 -46,24 -56,0 C -46,-24 -24,-50 0,-64 Z" fill="none" stroke="url(#cpiLemon)" stroke-width="1.8" opacity="0.9"/><path d="M 0,-50 C 18,-38 36,-18 44,0 C 36,18 18,38 0,50 C -18,38 -36,18 -44,0 C -36,-18 -18,-38 0,-50 Z" fill="none" stroke="url(#cpiMint)" stroke-width="1.6" opacity="0.88"/><path d="M 0,-36 C 14,-28 26,-12 32,0 C 26,12 14,28 0,36 C -14,28 -26,12 -32,0 C -26,-12 -14,-28 0,-36 Z" fill="none" stroke="url(#cpiSky)" stroke-width="1.4" opacity="0.85"/><path d="M 0,-24 C 10,-18 18,-8 22,0 C 18,8 10,18 0,24 C -10,18 -18,8 -22,0 C -18,-8 -10,-18 0,-24 Z" fill="none" stroke="url(#cpiLav)" stroke-width="1.2" opacity="0.82"/></g>
<!-- Counter-rotating rainbow ribbons at the outermost edge -->
<g class="cpi-ribbon" filter="url(#cpiGlow)"><path d="M 0,-96 A 96,96 0 0 1 96,0" fill="none" stroke="url(#cpiPink)" stroke-width="2.4" stroke-linecap="round" opacity="0.85"/><path d="M 96,0 A 96,96 0 0 1 0,96" fill="none" stroke="url(#cpiLemon)" stroke-width="2.4" stroke-linecap="round" opacity="0.85"/><path d="M 0,96 A 96,96 0 0 1 -96,0" fill="none" stroke="url(#cpiMint)" stroke-width="2.4" stroke-linecap="round" opacity="0.85"/><path d="M -96,0 A 96,96 0 0 1 0,-96" fill="none" stroke="url(#cpiLav)" stroke-width="2.4" stroke-linecap="round" opacity="0.85"/></g>
<!-- Toilet-water vortex — pastel rainbow swirl spinning at the bottom -->
<g class="cpi-vortex" filter="url(#cpiSoft)"><circle cx="0" cy="0" r="58" fill="url(#cpiVortexFill)"/><path d="M 50,0  C 50,28 28,50 0,50  C -28,50 -50,28 -50,0  C -50,-28 -28,-50 0,-50  C 28,-50 50,-28 50,0 Z" fill="none" stroke="url(#cpiPink)" stroke-width="1.6"/><path d="M 40,0  C 40,22 22,40 0,40  C -22,40 -40,22 -40,0  C -40,-22 -22,-40 0,-40  C 22,-40 40,-22 40,0 Z" fill="none" stroke="url(#cpiPeach)" stroke-width="1.3" opacity="0.9"/><path d="M 30,0  C 30,17 17,30 0,30  C -17,30 -30,17 -30,0  C -30,-17 -17,-30 0,-30  C 17,-30 30,-17 30,0 Z" fill="none" stroke="url(#cpiMint)" stroke-width="1.0" opacity="0.85"/><path d="M 22,0  C 22,12 12,22 0,22  C -12,22 -22,12 -22,0  C -22,-12 -12,-22 0,-22  C 12,-22 22,-12 22,0 Z" fill="none" stroke="url(#cpiSky)" stroke-width="0.8" opacity="0.8"/><circle cx="0" cy="0" r="14" fill="url(#cpiCore)"/><circle cx="0" cy="0" r="4" fill="rgba(255,255,250,1)"/></g>
<!-- Porcelain rim of the toilet bowl — we emerge through this -->
<g class="cpi-bowl"><circle cx="0" cy="0" r="86" fill="none" stroke="rgba(248,242,250,0.95)" stroke-width="6"/><circle cx="0" cy="0" r="86" fill="url(#cpiPorcelain)" opacity="0.18"/><circle cx="0" cy="0" r="79" fill="none" stroke="rgba(210,196,232,0.55)" stroke-width="1.2"/></g>
<!-- Splashing droplets — pastel rainbow flung outward as you surface -->
<g class="cpi-splash" filter="url(#cpiGlow)">
  <circle class="cpi-drop cpi-drop-1"  cx="0"   cy="-78" r="3.0" fill="#FFB2D9"/>
  <circle class="cpi-drop cpi-drop-2"  cx="42"  cy="-66" r="2.6" fill="#FFD2AA"/>
  <circle class="cpi-drop cpi-drop-3"  cx="72"  cy="-32" r="3.2" fill="#FFFAB2"/>
  <circle class="cpi-drop cpi-drop-4"  cx="80"  cy="14"  r="2.6" fill="#B2FFD2"/>
  <circle class="cpi-drop cpi-drop-5"  cx="58"  cy="56"  r="3.0" fill="#B2E1FF"/>
  <circle class="cpi-drop cpi-drop-6"  cx="18"  cy="78"  r="3.2" fill="#D2BEFF"/>
  <circle class="cpi-drop cpi-drop-7"  cx="-30" cy="74"  r="2.6" fill="#EBC8FA"/>
  <circle class="cpi-drop cpi-drop-8"  cx="-62" cy="50"  r="3.0" fill="#FFB2D9"/>
  <circle class="cpi-drop cpi-drop-9"  cx="-80" cy="6"   r="2.6" fill="#FFFAB2"/>
  <circle class="cpi-drop cpi-drop-10" cx="-70" cy="-40" r="3.2" fill="#B2FFD2"/>
  <circle class="cpi-drop cpi-drop-11" cx="-32" cy="-70" r="2.6" fill="#B2E1FF"/>
  <circle class="cpi-drop cpi-drop-12" cx="36"  cy="-82" r="3.0" fill="#D2BEFF"/>
</g>
</svg>
</div>]
<svg class="coach-beam" viewBox="0 0 300 36" width="100%" height="36" preserveAspectRatio="none"><defs><linearGradient id="wdA" x1="0" x2="1"><stop offset="0%" stop-color="#3a2408" stop-opacity="0"/><stop offset="10%" stop-color="#5c3810" stop-opacity="1"/><stop offset="90%" stop-color="#5c3810" stop-opacity="1"/><stop offset="100%" stop-color="#3a2408" stop-opacity="0"/></linearGradient><linearGradient id="wdB" x1="0" x2="1"><stop offset="0%" stop-color="#3a2408" stop-opacity="0"/><stop offset="10%" stop-color="#7a5220" stop-opacity="0.7"/><stop offset="90%" stop-color="#7a5220" stop-opacity="0.7"/><stop offset="100%" stop-color="#3a2408" stop-opacity="0"/></linearGradient><linearGradient id="brA" x1="0" x2="1"><stop offset="0%" stop-color="#c8922a" stop-opacity="0"/><stop offset="50%" stop-color="#c8922a" stop-opacity="0.7"/><stop offset="100%" stop-color="#c8922a" stop-opacity="0"/></linearGradient><linearGradient id="wdGrain" x1="0" y1="0" x2="0" y2="1"><stop offset="0%" stop-color="#7a5220" stop-opacity="0.2"/><stop offset="50%" stop-color="#5c3810" stop-opacity="0"/><stop offset="100%" stop-color="#7a5220" stop-opacity="0.15"/></linearGradient></defs><rect x="0" y="6" width="300" height="24" fill="url(#wdA)"/><rect x="0" y="6" width="300" height="24" fill="url(#wdGrain)"/><line x1="0" y1="6" x2="300" y2="6" stroke="url(#wdB)" stroke-width="1.2"/><line x1="0" y1="30" x2="300" y2="30" stroke="url(#wdB)" stroke-width="1.2"/><line x1="0" y1="18" x2="300" y2="18" stroke="url(#brA)" stroke-width="1.5"/><g opacity="0.4" stroke="#7a5220" stroke-width="0.4" fill="none"><line x1="30" y1="6" x2="32" y2="30"/><line x1="80" y1="6" x2="78" y2="30"/><line x1="130" y1="6" x2="131" y2="30"/><line x1="170" y1="6" x2="169" y2="30"/><line x1="220" y1="6" x2="222" y2="30"/><line x1="270" y1="6" x2="268" y2="30"/></g><circle cx="50" cy="18" r="4" fill="#c8922a" opacity="0.5"/><circle cx="50" cy="17" r="1.5" fill="#ffe090" opacity="0.35"/><g transform="translate(150,18)" opacity="0.55"><path d="M-8,-6 Q-9,2 -6,6 Q-3,10 0,10 Q3,10 6,6 Q9,2 8,-6" fill="none" stroke="#c8922a" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"/><circle cx="-8" cy="-6" r="1.5" fill="#c8922a"/><circle cx="8" cy="-6" r="1.5" fill="#c8922a"/></g><circle cx="250" cy="18" r="4" fill="#c8922a" opacity="0.5"/><circle cx="250" cy="17" r="1.5" fill="#ffe090" opacity="0.35"/></svg>
(set: $afterMidnight to true)\
<h2 class="venue-title">The Coach and Horses</h2>
<svg class="coach-beam-bottom" viewBox="0 0 300 36" width="100%" height="36" preserveAspectRatio="none"><defs><linearGradient id="wdC" x1="0" x2="1"><stop offset="0%" stop-color="#3a2408" stop-opacity="0"/><stop offset="10%" stop-color="#5c3810" stop-opacity="1"/><stop offset="90%" stop-color="#5c3810" stop-opacity="1"/><stop offset="100%" stop-color="#3a2408" stop-opacity="0"/></linearGradient><linearGradient id="wdD" x1="0" x2="1"><stop offset="0%" stop-color="#3a2408" stop-opacity="0"/><stop offset="10%" stop-color="#7a5220" stop-opacity="0.7"/><stop offset="90%" stop-color="#7a5220" stop-opacity="0.7"/><stop offset="100%" stop-color="#3a2408" stop-opacity="0"/></linearGradient><linearGradient id="brB" x1="0" x2="1"><stop offset="0%" stop-color="#c8922a" stop-opacity="0"/><stop offset="50%" stop-color="#c8922a" stop-opacity="0.7"/><stop offset="100%" stop-color="#c8922a" stop-opacity="0"/></linearGradient><linearGradient id="wdGrain2" x1="0" y1="0" x2="0" y2="1"><stop offset="0%" stop-color="#7a5220" stop-opacity="0.15"/><stop offset="50%" stop-color="#5c3810" stop-opacity="0"/><stop offset="100%" stop-color="#7a5220" stop-opacity="0.2"/></linearGradient></defs><rect x="0" y="6" width="300" height="24" fill="url(#wdC)"/><rect x="0" y="6" width="300" height="24" fill="url(#wdGrain2)"/><line x1="0" y1="6" x2="300" y2="6" stroke="url(#wdD)" stroke-width="1.2"/><line x1="0" y1="30" x2="300" y2="30" stroke="url(#wdD)" stroke-width="1.2"/><line x1="0" y1="18" x2="300" y2="18" stroke="url(#brB)" stroke-width="1.5"/><g opacity="0.4" stroke="#7a5220" stroke-width="0.4" fill="none"><line x1="35" y1="6" x2="33" y2="30"/><line x1="85" y1="6" x2="87" y2="30"/><line x1="135" y1="6" x2="134" y2="30"/><line x1="165" y1="6" x2="166" y2="30"/><line x1="215" y1="6" x2="213" y2="30"/><line x1="265" y1="6" x2="267" y2="30"/></g><circle cx="50" cy="18" r="4" fill="#c8922a" opacity="0.5"/><circle cx="50" cy="17" r="1.5" fill="#ffe090" opacity="0.35"/><circle cx="150" cy="18" r="4.5" fill="#c8922a" opacity="0.55"/><circle cx="150" cy="17" r="1.8" fill="#ffe090" opacity="0.4"/><circle cx="250" cy="18" r="4" fill="#c8922a" opacity="0.5"/><circle cx="250" cy="17" r="1.5" fill="#ffe090" opacity="0.35"/></svg>

(if: _lilyRing)[(set: $lilyCallReturn to "Coach and Horses lock")<div class="phone-ringing">A phone rings.

(link: "Accept the call")[(set: $confidence to ($statLoss: $confidence, 6))(go-to: "Lily phone call 1")]</div>]
(else-if: _dualRing)[(set: $lilyCallReturn to "Coach and Horses lock")<div class="phone-ringing">The phone behind the bar rings.

(link: "Accept the call")[(set: $confidence to ($statLoss: $confidence, 7))(go-to: "The dual ring")]</div>]
(else:)[(if: $resumingFromCall is true)[(set: $resumingFromCall to false)(if: $sobriety <= 15)[(link: "Retch.")[(set: $sobriety to ($statGain: $sobriety, 14))<script>setTimeout(function(){ window.showSpewPopup(); }, 200);</script>]]](else:)[You've come-to in a cubicle, in what you think is the gents in the Coach and Horses.

(if: $coachUrgent is true)[<span class="alba-link-fade">[[Give up. Sleep here.|Alba Incomplete]]</span>

]\
(if: $crashedAfterDualRing is true)[(link: "Retch.")[(set: $sobriety to ($statGain: $sobriety, 18))(set: $crashedAfterDualRing to false)<script>setTimeout(function(){ window.showSpewPopup(); }, 200);</script>]](else:)[(link: "Retch.")[(set: $sobriety to ($statGain: $sobriety, 14))<script>setTimeout(function(){ window.showSpewPopup(); }, 200);</script>]]

You gather your limbs to the bar.

The place is empty except for Jeffrey Bernard and, tall under the optics, his cow.

'You don't look well,' he says. 'Have you seen my cow?'

You heft your eyes to admire it, as he desires. He seems, for a moment, confused, then, owling his head in the direction you're looking, cries, 'There she is!'

She moos.

'And I don't want that book you've got, either. (if: $knowsLackland is false)[Speak to Lackland, he'll be about. ]You best find your own way out.'
(set: $knowsLackland to true)\
(set: $confidence to ($statGain: $confidence, 6))

'Will you please do something about this cow?'

You take its bridle. It sneezes. When you look back he's disappeared, perhaps to a timeshare on the seacoast of Bohemia.

(if: not ($haunts contains $haunt3))[
(set: $haunts to $haunts + (a: $haunt3))
<div class="haunt-box">
<div class="haunt-header">⟡ HAUNT COLLECTED ⟡</div>
<div class="haunt-name">THE BEAST</div>
<div class="haunt-description">Is it New York or New Year?</div>
<div class="haunt-work"><em>The work: Putrefactio.</em></div>
<div class="haunt-progress">(print: $haunts's length) of 12 caught</div>
</div>
(if: $haunts's length is 1)[(set: $hauntExplained to true)
<div class="lore-box">\
<strong>⟡ HAUNTS ⟡</strong>\
<p>Tonight, Soho will mark you. Here, in our mutual dream, we will call the marks 'haunts'. You'll gather them as you do the night's Great Work.</p>\
<div class="notebook-hint">↗ Saved to your notebook</div>\
<div class="notebook-hint">Collect more haunts to unlock the map.</div>\
</div>]]

What will you do with his cow?
]

[[Ride the beast|Ride Jeffrey Bernard's cow]]]

