]\
(if: $coachUrgent is false and $confidence <= 5)[[[Give up on the night|No more]]
]\
]

:: Dido [dream pyre] {"position":"100,1700","size":"100,100"}
(unless: $visitedPyre is a boolean)[(set: $visitedPyre to false)]\
(set: $visitedPyre to true)\
<svg class="carthage-pyre" viewBox="0 0 500 95" width="100%" height="95" preserveAspectRatio="none"><defs><radialGradient id="cpGlow" cx="50%" cy="88%" r="72%"><stop offset="0%" stop-color="#ffa040" stop-opacity="0.55"/><stop offset="18%" stop-color="#d4600a" stop-opacity="0.32"/><stop offset="55%" stop-color="#401808" stop-opacity="0.12"/><stop offset="100%" stop-color="#0a0a12" stop-opacity="0"/></radialGradient><radialGradient id="cpFlameCore" cx="50%" cy="80%" r="60%"><stop offset="0%" stop-color="#fff0d0" stop-opacity="0.85"/><stop offset="35%" stop-color="#ffc868" stop-opacity="0.55"/><stop offset="70%" stop-color="#e88020" stop-opacity="0.30"/><stop offset="100%" stop-color="#c84808" stop-opacity="0"/></radialGradient><linearGradient id="cpTopFade" x1="0" y1="0" x2="0" y2="1"><stop offset="0%" stop-color="#0a0a12" stop-opacity="1"/><stop offset="35%" stop-color="#0a0a12" stop-opacity="0.6"/><stop offset="60%" stop-color="#0a0a12" stop-opacity="0"/><stop offset="100%" stop-color="#0a0a12" stop-opacity="0"/></linearGradient><linearGradient id="cpFade" x1="0" x2="1"><stop offset="0%" stop-color="#0a0a12" stop-opacity="1"/><stop offset="8%" stop-color="#0a0a12" stop-opacity="0"/><stop offset="92%" stop-color="#0a0a12" stop-opacity="0"/><stop offset="100%" stop-color="#0a0a12" stop-opacity="1"/></linearGradient><linearGradient id="cpGround" x1="0" y1="0" x2="0" y2="1"><stop offset="0%" stop-color="#3a2010" stop-opacity="0.5"/><stop offset="100%" stop-color="#1a0a08" stop-opacity="0.3"/></linearGradient><linearGradient id="cpLogDark" x1="0" y1="0" x2="0" y2="1"><stop offset="0%" stop-color="#3a1a08"/><stop offset="100%" stop-color="#140804"/></linearGradient><linearGradient id="cpLogGlow" x1="0" y1="0" x2="0" y2="1"><stop offset="0%" stop-color="#502410"/><stop offset="55%" stop-color="#c84808" stop-opacity="0.85"/><stop offset="100%" stop-color="#3a1808"/></linearGradient><linearGradient id="cpShroud" x1="0" y1="0" x2="0" y2="1"><stop offset="0%" stop-color="#2a1208"/><stop offset="100%" stop-color="#0a0402"/></linearGradient><linearGradient id="cpColumn" x1="0" y1="0" x2="0" y2="1"><stop offset="0%" stop-color="#7a5a3a"/><stop offset="100%" stop-color="#3a2818"/></linearGradient></defs><!-- Warm glow over the scene --><rect x="0" y="0" width="500" height="95" fill="url(#cpGlow)"/><!-- Ground --><rect x="0" y="80" width="500" height="15" fill="url(#cpGround)"/><!-- Distant ruin shapes on the horizon --><path d="M140,80 L142,55 L145,58 L148,52 L152,60 L156,55 L159,80 Z" fill="#2a1810" opacity="0.55"/><path d="M338,80 L341,48 L347,53 L351,46 L355,56 L359,50 L362,80 Z" fill="#2a1810" opacity="0.5"/><path d="M168,80 L171,68 L177,72 L180,80 Z" fill="#2a1810" opacity="0.42"/><path d="M324,80 L327,71 L332,75 L336,80 Z" fill="#2a1810" opacity="0.42"/><!-- Far-left broken column with fluting --><g opacity="0.7"><rect x="78" y="32" width="6" height="48" fill="url(#cpColumn)"/><line x1="79.5" y1="34" x2="79.5" y2="78" stroke="#1a0e06" stroke-width="0.35" opacity="0.55"/><line x1="81" y1="34" x2="81" y2="78" stroke="#1a0e06" stroke-width="0.35" opacity="0.5"/><line x1="82.5" y1="34" x2="82.5" y2="78" stroke="#1a0e06" stroke-width="0.35" opacity="0.55"/><rect x="76" y="29" width="10" height="4" rx="0.5" fill="#806858"/><path d="M76,32 L86,29 L86,33 L76,36 Z" fill="#806858" opacity="0.6"/><!-- Fallen drum next to base --><ellipse cx="73" cy="80" rx="8" ry="2" fill="#3a2818" opacity="0.5"/><rect x="67" y="77" width="12" height="3.5" rx="0.5" fill="#806858" opacity="0.5"/><circle cx="69" cy="78.5" r="1.5" fill="#3a2010" opacity="0.65"/></g><!-- Far-right column — taller, slightly more eroded --><g opacity="0.65"><rect x="402" y="22" width="6" height="58" fill="url(#cpColumn)"/><line x1="403.5" y1="25" x2="403.5" y2="78" stroke="#1a0e06" stroke-width="0.35" opacity="0.55"/><line x1="405" y1="25" x2="405" y2="78" stroke="#1a0e06" stroke-width="0.35" opacity="0.5"/><line x1="406.5" y1="25" x2="406.5" y2="78" stroke="#1a0e06" stroke-width="0.35" opacity="0.55"/><rect x="400" y="19" width="10" height="4" rx="0.5" fill="#806858"/><!-- Crack running down --><path d="M404,38 Q406,46 404,54 Q406,62 404,70" fill="none" stroke="#0a0402" stroke-width="0.5" opacity="0.55"/><!-- Lichen patch --><ellipse cx="407" cy="50" rx="1.8" ry="3.5" fill="#3a4828" opacity="0.4"/><!-- Rubble at base --><ellipse cx="416" cy="80" rx="10" ry="2.5" fill="#3a2818" opacity="0.45"/><rect x="408" y="76" width="8" height="4" rx="0.5" fill="#806858" opacity="0.5"/><circle cx="420" cy="79" r="1.7" fill="#3a2010" opacity="0.6"/></g><!-- ============================================================ --><!--   THE PYRE — built up of charred logs, body shrouded on top      --><!-- ============================================================ --><!-- Shadow on ground --><ellipse cx="250" cy="82" rx="72" ry="3.5" fill="#0a0402" opacity="0.65"/><!-- Bottom log course (long, dark, charred) --><rect x="190" y="74" width="120" height="6" rx="1.5" fill="url(#cpLogDark)"/><rect x="190" y="74" width="120" height="2" fill="#5a2010" opacity="0.55"/><!-- Log end-grain on each end --><circle cx="192" cy="77" r="2.6" fill="#3a1408"/><circle cx="192" cy="77" r="1.6" fill="#0a0402"/><circle cx="308" cy="77" r="2.6" fill="#3a1408"/><circle cx="308" cy="77" r="1.6" fill="#0a0402"/><!-- Cross-grain split lines --><line x1="210" y1="74" x2="210" y2="80" stroke="#0a0402" stroke-width="0.4" opacity="0.6"/><line x1="232" y1="74" x2="232" y2="80" stroke="#0a0402" stroke-width="0.4" opacity="0.55"/><line x1="252" y1="74" x2="252" y2="80" stroke="#0a0402" stroke-width="0.4" opacity="0.6"/><line x1="270" y1="74" x2="270" y2="80" stroke="#0a0402" stroke-width="0.4" opacity="0.55"/><line x1="288" y1="74" x2="288" y2="80" stroke="#0a0402" stroke-width="0.4" opacity="0.6"/><!-- Second course (perpendicular, inset) --><rect x="202" y="68" width="96" height="6" rx="1" fill="url(#cpLogDark)"/><rect x="202" y="68" width="96" height="2" fill="#5a2010" opacity="0.55"/><line x1="220" y1="68" x2="220" y2="74" stroke="#0a0402" stroke-width="0.4" opacity="0.55"/><line x1="245" y1="68" x2="245" y2="74" stroke="#0a0402" stroke-width="0.4" opacity="0.55"/><line x1="275" y1="68" x2="275" y2="74" stroke="#0a0402" stroke-width="0.4" opacity="0.55"/><!-- Third course (top course, glowing — body rests on this) --><rect x="212" y="62" width="76" height="6" rx="1" fill="url(#cpLogGlow)"/><rect x="212" y="62" width="76" height="1.5" fill="#3a1408" opacity="0.5"/><line x1="232" y1="62" x2="232" y2="68" stroke="#1a0a04" stroke-width="0.4" opacity="0.65"/><line x1="252" y1="62" x2="252" y2="68" stroke="#1a0a04" stroke-width="0.4" opacity="0.65"/><line x1="270" y1="62" x2="270" y2="68" stroke="#1a0a04" stroke-width="0.4" opacity="0.65"/><!-- Glowing embers visible between top logs --><ellipse cx="240" cy="68.5" rx="3" ry="0.8" fill="#ff8030" opacity="0.85"/><ellipse cx="262" cy="68.5" rx="2.4" ry="0.7" fill="#ffa040" opacity="0.8"/><ellipse cx="252" cy="68.5" rx="1.5" ry="0.6" fill="#fff0c0" opacity="0.7"/><!-- ────────────  BODY — shrouded, lying on the top course ──────────── --><!-- Main shroud body (lying horizontal across the logs) --><path d="M210,62 Q210,56 215,55 L285,55 Q290,56 290,62 Z" fill="url(#cpShroud)"/><!-- Body subtle shadow folds --><path d="M222,57 Q226,59 234,56 Q244,59 254,56 Q264,59 274,56 Q280,59 285,57" fill="none" stroke="#3a1810" stroke-width="0.7" opacity="0.55"/><!-- Head (left end, slightly raised) --><ellipse cx="212" cy="55" rx="6" ry="4.5" fill="#1a0a04"/><ellipse cx="211" cy="54" rx="2" ry="1.5" fill="#3a1810" opacity="0.6"/><!-- Foot end --><ellipse cx="288" cy="56" rx="4" ry="3.2" fill="#1a0a04"/><!-- Funeral cloth at the top edge — darker line --><line x1="208" y1="55" x2="290" y2="55" stroke="#0a0402" stroke-width="0.6" opacity="0.85"/><!-- ────────────  FLAMES — layered, rising around body ──────────── --><!-- Outer flame envelope (broad soft glow) --><ellipse cx="250" cy="46" rx="44" ry="38" fill="url(#cpFlameCore)" opacity="0.85"/><!-- Layer 1 — deep red outer --><path d="M208,62 Q198,40 218,16 Q224,28 230,4 Q236,22 242,2 Q248,22 252,1 Q256,22 262,3 Q268,22 274,8 Q280,28 286,16 Q300,38 292,62Z" fill="#8a2800" opacity="0.62"/><!-- Layer 2 — bright orange mid --><path d="M216,62 Q208,42 224,20 Q232,32 240,10 Q245,26 250,5 Q256,26 261,10 Q267,32 274,18 Q284,36 280,62Z" fill="#c04808" opacity="0.72"/><!-- Layer 3 — orange brighter --><path d="M224,62 Q220,44 232,26 Q238,36 244,14 Q248,28 252,10 Q257,28 262,14 Q268,32 275,28 Q282,46 272,62Z" fill="#d4600a" opacity="0.78"/><!-- Layer 4 — yellow inner --><path d="M232,62 Q228,46 238,30 Q242,40 246,20 Q250,30 254,18 Q258,30 262,22 Q268,38 266,62Z" fill="#e88020" opacity="0.75"/><!-- Layer 5 — bright yellow tongue --><path d="M238,62 Q237,48 242,34 Q246,40 250,28 Q254,40 257,28 Q260,42 261,62Z" fill="#ffa040" opacity="0.68"/><!-- Layer 6 — white-hot core --><path d="M244,62 Q243,50 248,38 Q250,46 252,38 Q254,46 256,62Z" fill="#ffc868" opacity="0.62"/><!-- White-hot tip --><ellipse cx="251" cy="42" rx="2.5" ry="5.5" fill="#fff0d0" opacity="0.55"/><!-- Side wisps (left and right) --><path d="M204,62 Q198,52 205,38 Q208,48 213,52 Q210,58 214,62Z" fill="#8a2800" opacity="0.45"/><path d="M296,62 Q302,52 295,38 Q292,48 287,52 Q290,58 286,62Z" fill="#8a2800" opacity="0.45"/><!-- Small lick on far left --><path d="M212,62 Q207,55 211,46 Q214,52 215,62Z" fill="#c04808" opacity="0.5"/><path d="M288,62 Q293,55 289,46 Q286,52 285,62Z" fill="#c04808" opacity="0.5"/><!-- ────────────  RISING EMBERS — many, varied glowing sparks ──────────── --><circle cx="245" cy="6" r="1.2" fill="#ffc868" opacity="0.9"/><circle cx="245" cy="6" r="0.5" fill="#fff0d0" opacity="0.95"/><circle cx="260" cy="9" r="0.9" fill="#ff8030" opacity="0.85"/><circle cx="238" cy="11" r="1" fill="#ffa040" opacity="0.85"/><circle cx="268" cy="3" r="0.65" fill="#ffc868" opacity="0.85"/><circle cx="252" cy="2" r="0.75" fill="#fff0d0" opacity="0.9"/><circle cx="229" cy="7" r="0.7" fill="#ff8030" opacity="0.8"/><circle cx="273" cy="13" r="1.1" fill="#ffa040" opacity="0.85"/><circle cx="242" cy="18" r="0.6" fill="#ffc868" opacity="0.8"/><circle cx="257" cy="16" r="0.55" fill="#ff6020" opacity="0.8"/><circle cx="223" cy="14" r="0.45" fill="#ff8030" opacity="0.7"/><circle cx="278" cy="20" r="0.75" fill="#ffc868" opacity="0.8"/><circle cx="217" cy="22" r="0.55" fill="#ffa040" opacity="0.7"/><circle cx="285" cy="27" r="0.5" fill="#ff8030" opacity="0.65"/><circle cx="248" cy="22" r="0.45" fill="#fff0d0" opacity="0.8"/><circle cx="234" cy="29" r="0.55" fill="#ff8030" opacity="0.6"/><circle cx="266" cy="29" r="0.45" fill="#ffc868" opacity="0.6"/><circle cx="226" cy="35" r="0.35" fill="#d4600a" opacity="0.55"/><circle cx="276" cy="35" r="0.4" fill="#ff8030" opacity="0.55"/><!-- ────────────  SMOKE WISPS — drift up off the highest flames ──────────── --><path d="M248,2 Q252,-3 246,-9" fill="none" stroke="#3a2a22" stroke-width="2.2" opacity="0.4" stroke-linecap="round"/><path d="M253,4 Q258,-2 251,-12" fill="none" stroke="#3a2a22" stroke-width="1.7" opacity="0.35" stroke-linecap="round"/><path d="M255,8 Q263,2 260,-7" fill="none" stroke="#3a2a22" stroke-width="1.4" opacity="0.3" stroke-linecap="round"/><!-- ────────────  GROUND EMBERS — small glowing dots on the ground around the pyre ──────────── --><circle cx="180" cy="83" r="0.8" fill="#d4600a" opacity="0.45"/><circle cx="320" cy="81" r="0.6" fill="#c84a08" opacity="0.4"/><circle cx="200" cy="84" r="0.4" fill="#ff8030" opacity="0.35"/><circle cx="305" cy="83" r="0.7" fill="#d4600a" opacity="0.45"/><circle cx="225" cy="85" r="0.35" fill="#ff8020" opacity="0.3"/><circle cx="275" cy="84" r="0.45" fill="#ff8030" opacity="0.35"/><circle cx="160" cy="84" r="0.5" fill="#ff8020" opacity="0.25"/><circle cx="340" cy="83" r="0.7" fill="#d4600a" opacity="0.3"/><circle cx="195" cy="82" r="0.3" fill="#ffa040" opacity="0.4"/><circle cx="313" cy="84" r="0.4" fill="#ff8030" opacity="0.35"/><!-- Edge fades to blend with surrounding prose --><rect x="0" y="0" width="500" height="95" fill="url(#cpTopFade)"/><rect x="0" y="0" width="500" height="95" fill="url(#cpFade)"/></svg>

On the pyre, Dido is burning where she has burnt for 2,000 years.

The scent of her sour embers means something about lily of the valley.

(if: $hasMissingPage is false and $returnedPage is false)['Stay,' she says, 'My Carthage is meant for you. Lily is in her valley and will not return. Rest here and think no more about England.']\
(else:)['You're back,' she says. 'Carthage was always meant for you. What you took from the fire is yours; there is nothing else here. Lily is in her valley. Lie down beside me, now.']

(link: "⟡ LORE: Her Dying Words ⟡")[<div class="dido-words"><span class="latin">Littora littoribus contraria, fluctibus undas<br>
Impresor: arma armis: pugnent ipsig nepotes:<br>
Liue false Æneas, truest Dido dyes,<br>
Sic sic inuat ire sub umbras.</span>
<hr class="didoRule">
<span class="english">Shores against shores; waves, waves;<br>
I curse, arms against arms, you and your children.<br>
Live false Aeneus, truest Dido dies,<br>
So, so happily I go, under shades.</span></div>]

(if: $knowsAboutPage is true and $hasMissingPage is false)[Among the flames, you see something that shouldn't be there — a page, curling at the edges but not yet consumed. The writing on it shifts and writhes.

[[Reach into the flames|Rescue the page]]]

(set: _carthageDone to ($alba contains $alba2) and ($hasMissingPage is true or $returnedPage is true))\
(if: _carthageDone)[\
The fire will burn without you now. The only way back is up.

<span class="guided-link">[[Wake from this dream|The Interval]]</span>

[[Sub umbras: watch her burn|Stay in Carthage]]
](else-if: $hasMissingPage is true or $returnedPage is true)[<span class="guided-link">[[Sub umbras: watch her burn|Stay in Carthage]]</span>]
(else:)[(if: ($haunts's length >= 3) and ($hasMissingPage is true or $returnedPage is true) and not ($alba contains $alba2))[[[Try The Green Sea|Green Sea Approach]]]

(if: $confidence <= 15)[[[Return to the shore|The coast of Carthage]]](else:)[(if: $haunts's length >= 3)[[[Go back to shore|Carthage shore]]](else:)[[[Wake from this dream|The Interval]]]]

(unless: $knowsAboutPage is true and $hasMissingPage is false)[[[Sub umbras: watch her burn|Stay in Carthage]]]]

:: Entering The Pillars of Hercules [venue-pillars] {"position":"300,1100","size":"100,100"}
(set: _lilyRing to ($lilyCount >= 1 and $hadLilyCall1 is false and $hadPhoneCall is true and ($returns - $phoneCallReturnsAt) >= 1 and $visited contains "Pillars" and $visited's Pillars is true))\
(set: _dualRing to ($lilyCount >= 2 and $hadLilyCall1 is true and $hadDualRing is false and ($returns - $lilyCall1ReturnsAt) >= 2 and $visited contains "Pillars" and $visited's Pillars is true))\
<div class="pillars-scene">
<div class="pillars-light"></div>
<div class="pillars-smoke"></div>
<div class="pillars-dust"><span style="left:12%;bottom:18%;animation-duration:7s;animation-delay:0s;"></span><span style="left:32%;bottom:8%;animation-duration:9.5s;animation-delay:1.2s;"></span><span style="left:52%;bottom:28%;animation-duration:6.5s;animation-delay:2.8s;"></span><span style="left:72%;bottom:5%;animation-duration:11s;animation-delay:0.4s;"></span><span style="left:22%;bottom:38%;animation-duration:8.5s;animation-delay:1.8s;"></span><span style="left:82%;bottom:22%;animation-duration:10s;animation-delay:3.5s;"></span><span style="left:42%;bottom:12%;animation-duration:7.8s;animation-delay:0.8s;"></span><span style="left:62%;bottom:32%;animation-duration:9s;animation-delay:2.2s;"></span></div>
<!-- Left broken pillar — Piranesi/Decline & Fall style -->
<svg class="pillar left" viewBox="0 0 34 280" preserveAspectRatio="xMidYMax meet"><defs><linearGradient id="pf" x1="0" x2="0" y1="0" y2="1"><stop offset="0%"   stop-color="#8ac8dc" stop-opacity="0.72"/><stop offset="60%"  stop-color="#8ac8dc" stop-opacity="0.42"/><stop offset="100%" stop-color="#8ac8dc" stop-opacity="0"/></linearGradient></defs><!-- Two-step plinth base --><rect x="1"  y="252" width="32" height="8"  fill="none" stroke="url(#pf)" stroke-width="1.1"/><rect x="4"  y="246" width="26" height="7"  fill="none" stroke="url(#pf)" stroke-width="1"/><!-- Shaft edges (slight taper: 24px wide at top, 26px at base) --><line x1="5"  y1="246" x2="6"  y2="88" stroke="url(#pf)" stroke-width="1.1"/><line x1="29" y1="246" x2="28" y2="88" stroke="url(#pf)" stroke-width="1.1"/><!-- Drum course bands every 22px --><line x1="5.3" y1="110" x2="28.7" y2="110" stroke="url(#pf)" stroke-width="0.65"/><line x1="5.5" y1="132" x2="28.5" y2="132" stroke="url(#pf)" stroke-width="0.65"/><line x1="5.5" y1="154" x2="28.5" y2="154" stroke="url(#pf)" stroke-width="0.65"/><line x1="5.5" y1="176" x2="28.5" y2="176" stroke="url(#pf)" stroke-width="0.65"/><line x1="5.5" y1="198" x2="28.5" y2="198" stroke="url(#pf)" stroke-width="0.65"/><line x1="5.5" y1="220" x2="28.5" y2="220" stroke="url(#pf)" stroke-width="0.65"/><line x1="5.5" y1="242" x2="28.5" y2="242" stroke="url(#pf)" stroke-width="0.65"/><!-- Faint fluting --><line x1="10" y1="88" x2="10" y2="245" stroke="#8ac8dc" stroke-width="0.3" opacity="0.22"/><line x1="14" y1="88" x2="14" y2="245" stroke="#8ac8dc" stroke-width="0.3" opacity="0.22"/><line x1="17" y1="88" x2="17" y2="245" stroke="#8ac8dc" stroke-width="0.3" opacity="0.22"/><line x1="20" y1="88" x2="20" y2="245" stroke="#8ac8dc" stroke-width="0.3" opacity="0.22"/><line x1="24" y1="88" x2="24" y2="245" stroke="#8ac8dc" stroke-width="0.3" opacity="0.22"/><!-- Echinus (curved capital swell) --><path d="M6,88 Q5,78 3,72 L31,72 Q29,78 28,88" fill="none" stroke="url(#pf)" stroke-width="1.1"/><!-- Abacus slab — CRACKED, left portion collapsed inward --><!-- Right surviving portion: tilting down-left --><path d="M12,72 L32,68 L33,63 L13,66 Z" fill="none" stroke="#8ac8dc" stroke-width="1" opacity="0.6"/><!-- Left fallen piece: a slab lying at an angle, partly off the shaft --><path d="M2,74 L-2,70 L8,67 L11,72 Z" fill="none" stroke="#8ac8dc" stroke-width="0.9" opacity="0.45"/><!-- Fracture line across shaft top --><path d="M6,88 L9,83 L13,87 L17,80 L21,86 L25,79 L28,88" fill="none" stroke="#8ac8dc" stroke-width="0.9" opacity="0.55"/><!-- A fallen drum section leaning against the shaft at ~1/3 height --><path d="M1,168 L3,160 L9,162 L9,170 L3,172 Z" fill="none" stroke="#8ac8dc" stroke-width="0.85" opacity="0.32"/><!-- Crack on shaft face --><path d="M13,130 L15,142 L12,150" fill="none" stroke="#8ac8dc" stroke-width="0.5" opacity="0.28"/><!-- Rubble at base --><path d="M3,255  L9,255  L10,260 L2,260 Z"  fill="none" stroke="#8ac8dc" stroke-width="0.8" opacity="0.28"/><path d="M21,257 L28,257 L29,262 L20,261 Z" fill="none" stroke="#8ac8dc" stroke-width="0.7" opacity="0.22"/><path d="M13,260 L18,259 L19,264 L12,263 Z" fill="none" stroke="#8ac8dc" stroke-width="0.7" opacity="0.2"/></svg>
<!-- Right pillar — same shape, scaleX(-1) mirrors it so break faces inward -->
<svg class="pillar right" viewBox="0 0 34 280" preserveAspectRatio="xMidYMax meet"><defs><linearGradient id="pf2" x1="0" x2="0" y1="0" y2="1"><stop offset="0%"   stop-color="#8ac8dc" stop-opacity="0.72"/><stop offset="60%"  stop-color="#8ac8dc" stop-opacity="0.42"/><stop offset="100%" stop-color="#8ac8dc" stop-opacity="0"/></linearGradient></defs><rect x="1"  y="252" width="32" height="8"  fill="none" stroke="url(#pf2)" stroke-width="1.1"/><rect x="4"  y="246" width="26" height="7"  fill="none" stroke="url(#pf2)" stroke-width="1"/><!-- Shorter shaft: top at y=130 instead of y=88 — this pillar more ruined --><line x1="5"  y1="246" x2="6"  y2="130" stroke="url(#pf2)" stroke-width="1.1"/><line x1="29" y1="246" x2="28" y2="130" stroke="url(#pf2)" stroke-width="1.1"/><line x1="5.5" y1="152" x2="28.5" y2="152" stroke="url(#pf2)" stroke-width="0.65"/><line x1="5.5" y1="174" x2="28.5" y2="174" stroke="url(#pf2)" stroke-width="0.65"/><line x1="5.5" y1="196" x2="28.5" y2="196" stroke="url(#pf2)" stroke-width="0.65"/><line x1="5.5" y1="218" x2="28.5" y2="218" stroke="url(#pf2)" stroke-width="0.65"/><line x1="5.5" y1="240" x2="28.5" y2="240" stroke="url(#pf2)" stroke-width="0.65"/><line x1="10" y1="130" x2="10" y2="245" stroke="#8ac8dc" stroke-width="0.3" opacity="0.22"/><line x1="14" y1="130" x2="14" y2="245" stroke="#8ac8dc" stroke-width="0.3" opacity="0.22"/><line x1="17" y1="130" x2="17" y2="245" stroke="#8ac8dc" stroke-width="0.3" opacity="0.22"/><line x1="20" y1="130" x2="20" y2="245" stroke="#8ac8dc" stroke-width="0.3" opacity="0.22"/><line x1="24" y1="130" x2="24" y2="245" stroke="#8ac8dc" stroke-width="0.3" opacity="0.22"/><!-- Echinus at top of shorter shaft --><path d="M6,130 Q5,120 3,114 L31,114 Q29,120 28,130" fill="none" stroke="url(#pf2)" stroke-width="1.1"/><!-- This column: abacus has COLLAPSED entirely — jagged stump and tilted block --><path d="M3,114 L6,107 L10,112 L14,104 L18,110 L22,102 L27,108 L31,114" fill="none" stroke="#8ac8dc" stroke-width="1" opacity="0.6"/><!-- Large fallen capital block --><path d="M2,106 L-3,98 L14,94 L17,104 Z" fill="none" stroke="#8ac8dc" stroke-width="1" opacity="0.5"/><!-- Fracture running down shaft --><path d="M6,130 L9,125 L13,129 L17,122 L21,128 L25,121 L28,130" fill="none" stroke="#8ac8dc" stroke-width="0.9" opacity="0.55"/><path d="M9,142 L11,158 L8,164" fill="none" stroke="#8ac8dc" stroke-width="0.5" opacity="0.28"/><!-- Fallen drum leaning against shaft --><path d="M1,215 L3,207 L9,209 L9,217 L3,219 Z" fill="none" stroke="#8ac8dc" stroke-width="0.85" opacity="0.3"/><!-- Rubble at base --><path d="M3,255 L9,255 L10,260 L2,260 Z"    fill="none" stroke="#8ac8dc" stroke-width="0.8" opacity="0.28"/><path d="M22,257 L29,257 L30,262 L21,261 Z"  fill="none" stroke="#8ac8dc" stroke-width="0.7" opacity="0.22"/><path d="M11,260 L17,259 L18,264 L10,263 Z"  fill="none" stroke="#8ac8dc" stroke-width="0.7" opacity="0.2"/></svg>
<!-- Lattice pub window at top -->
<svg class="pillars-lattice" viewBox="0 0 300 36" width="100%" height="36" preserveAspectRatio="none"><defs><linearGradient id="latEdge" x1="0" x2="1"><stop offset="0%"   stop-color="#7ab8cc" stop-opacity="0"/><stop offset="15%"  stop-color="#7ab8cc" stop-opacity="0.55"/><stop offset="85%"  stop-color="#7ab8cc" stop-opacity="0.55"/><stop offset="100%" stop-color="#7ab8cc" stop-opacity="0"/></linearGradient><pattern id="dLat" x="0" y="0" width="42" height="24" patternUnits="userSpaceOnUse"><path d="M7,0 L14,12 L7,24 L0,12 Z" fill="rgba(160,35,25,0.26)" stroke="#5a96aa" stroke-width="1" stroke-linejoin="round"/><path d="M21,0 L28,12 L21,24 L14,12 Z" fill="rgba(185,215,235,0.07)" stroke="#5a96aa" stroke-width="1" stroke-linejoin="round"/><path d="M35,0 L42,12 L35,24 L28,12 Z" fill="rgba(28,108,52,0.22)" stroke="#5a96aa" stroke-width="1" stroke-linejoin="round"/></pattern><mask id="latMask"><rect x="0" y="0" width="300" height="36" fill="url(#latEdge)"/></mask></defs><rect x="0" y="0" width="300" height="36" fill="url(#dLat)" mask="url(#latMask)"/><line x1="0" y1="34" x2="300" y2="34" stroke="url(#latEdge)" stroke-width="1.2"/></svg>
(unless: $visited is a datamap)[(set: $visited to (dm:))]\
(unless: $visited contains "Pillars")[(set: $visited's Pillars to false)]\
(if: $resumingFromCall is true)[(set: $resumingFromCall to false)](else:)[(set: $sobriety to ($statLoss: $sobriety, 9))\
(if: $visited's Pillars is false)[(set: $visited's Pillars to true)\
(set: $confidence to ($statGain: $confidence, 12))]]\
If you cross the threshold of the Pillars you've already made your choice.

Whatever more you choose comes out in the wash:

(if: _lilyRing)[(set: $lilyCallReturn to "Entering The Pillars of Hercules")<div class="phone-ringing">A phone rings.

(link: "Accept the call")[(set: $confidence to ($statLoss: $confidence, 6))(go-to: "Lily phone call 1")]</div>]
(else-if: _dualRing)[(set: $lilyCallReturn to "Entering The Pillars of Hercules")<div class="phone-ringing">The phone behind the bar rings.

(link: "Accept the call")[(set: $confidence to ($statLoss: $confidence, 7))(go-to: "The dual ring")]</div>]
(else:)[(if: $hadPhoneCall is true and $metCritic is true and $tookLily2 is false)[<span class="dss-flower-only-marker"></span>](if: $tookLily2 is false)[|lily2>[(display: "Lily SVG")]\
(click-replace: ?lily2)[(set: $lilyCount to $lilyCount + 1)(set: $tookLily2 to true)(display: "Lily SVG")<span class="lily-glimpse lily-fade">There occurs, as you cross the threshold of the Pillars, a sonic peculiarity seen elsewhere, for instance, in the acoustic mirrors on Dungeness. If you stand in that precise spot and the atmospherics are favourable, you might hear a noise made at that same instant anywhere in Soho. You hear Lily laugh.</span>(if: $lilyHintShown is false)[(set: $lilyHintShown to true)<div class="lily-glimpse-hint">(Gather flowers. There are five to find.)</div>](if: $lilyCount is 5)[(set: $confidence to ($statGain: $confidence, 25))(set: $sobriety to ($statGain: $sobriety, 15))<div class="pent-reveal-note"><div class="pent-reveal-title">⛤ THE PENTACLE ⛤</div><div class="pent-reveal-body">Five flowers, five points; the city draws its star around you.</div><span class="inventory-note">&#9734; MORALE +25 | SOBRIETY +15</span></div><script>setTimeout(function(){if(window.dssRevealPentangleOnMap)window.dssRevealPentangleOnMap();},900);</script>]]](else:)[<div class="lily-taken">(display: "Lily SVG")</div>]

<div class="verse">Hobson has supt, and 's newly gon to bed.</div>
(if: $hadPhoneCall is false)[<div class="phone-ringing">Behind the bar a phone rings and your name is called.

(link: "Accept the call")[(set: $confidence to ($statLoss: $confidence, 9))(go-to: "The phone call")]</div>]
(else-if: $metCritic is false)[Through the fumes, vapours and drink, you recognise a man.

(link: "⟡ LORE: The Great Ham ⟡")[<div class="lore-box">
<strong>⟡ THE GREAT HAM ⟡</strong>

<div class="editors-note">
<span class="editors-note-label">Editor's note</span>
When Dr. Johnson, the harmless drudge and titan nonpareil among the London's literati in the mid-eighteenth century, was at the height of his powers, he was called the Great Cham. (Cham being a variant of Khan, that is: supreme leader).

When Ian Hamilton occupied a similar position, two centuries later, nobody (I am sadly but reliably informed) bestowed on him the obvious sobriquet. Here I intend to fix that.
</div>
</div>]
[[Talk to the Great Ham|Talk to the critic]]]
(else:)[The room hums on without you. Your business here is finished.

[[Back to Dean Street|Dean Street]]]]
</div>

:: Standing [venue-cellar] {"position":"2200,1350","size":"100,100"}
<!-- Swinging bulb -->
<div class="cellar-bulb-wrap">
<svg width="48" height="90" viewBox="0 0 48 90"><line x1="24" y1="0" x2="24" y2="30" stroke="#888878" stroke-width="1.4" opacity="0.75"/><rect x="17" y="28" width="14" height="10" rx="2.5"fill="rgba(80,78,65,0.9)" stroke="rgba(160,155,120,0.7)" stroke-width="1"/><rect x="19" y="36" width="10" height="3" rx="1"fill="none" stroke="rgba(150,145,110,0.55)" stroke-width="0.8"/><ellipse cx="24" cy="60" rx="20" ry="22"fill="rgba(255,245,160,0.12)"/><path d="M24,38 C16,38 10,45 10,55 C10,67 16,78 24,78 C32,78 38,67 38,55 C38,45 32,38 24,38 Z"fill="rgba(255,252,210,0.95)" stroke="rgba(220,210,160,0.6)" stroke-width="0.8"/><ellipse cx="24" cy="57" rx="9" ry="11"fill="rgba(255,240,120,0.55)"/><path d="M18,60 L20,53 L24,58 L28,53 L30,60"fill="none" stroke="rgba(255,200,40,0.95)" stroke-width="1.4" stroke-linejoin="round"/><rect x="20" y="75" width="8" height="3" rx="1"fill="rgba(200,195,155,0.65)" stroke="none"/></svg>
</div>
<div class="cellar-scene">
<div class="cellar-light"></div>

You bolt for the stairs. Copper calls after you — half-genial, half-mocking — but you're long gone, back through the door.

And through the door, leaning its knackered frame against his own, is John St. John.

'You lead a charmed life,' he says.

John falls in beside you as you push out onto Dean Street: 'Red told Copper you had money.'

You're lucky, you reflect, that he worked out you don't.

[[Back to Dean Street|The dark pass]]
</div>

:: The dark pass [outdoor] {"position":"2300,1350","size":"100,100"}
<div class="typewriter-page">
You watch John St. John throw off his tail in the darkness, then surface again at the far end of the street, in the pool where the ginger light shines.

Just as he does, Red walks into the frame, hands deep in his pockets; fag in his mouth, swaying like a conductor's baton.

It seems, almost, like Red wants to speak to John, who doesn't want to speak to anybody, and so ploughs his long stride deeper and into the night.

[[Dean Street|Dean Street]]
</div>
<script>
// Light a cigarette of your own — Red is smoking, John has gone, you're
// alone on Dean Street and your hands need something to do. Auto-shows
// after the prose has had a beat to settle.
(function(){
  var pgGen = window._passageGen;
  setTimeout(function(){
    if (window._passageGen !== pgGen) return;
    if (window.showCigarettePopup) window.showCigarettePopup();
  }, 5500);
})();
</script>

:: Failure: Trisha's {"position":"700,1400","size":"100,100"}
(if: $hasTrishaMatchbook is true)[The doorman's saying no tonight. You're about to fuck off, politely, when you think of the matchbook. You give it him. 'Jack Curtis,' he says. 'You should have said. Come in.'

[[Enter Trisha's|Trisha's]]]\
(else:)[(set: $confidence to ($statLoss: $confidence, 11))

They do not know you.

[[Dean Street|Dean Street]]]

