<span id="tarot-continue" style="display:none">
'You do not find the Hanged Man.'

'What's wrong with it?' she asks.

[[What?|Shana's Verdict]]
</span>

<script>
(function(){
var flipped=[false,false,false];
window.dssFlipCard=function(n){
var card=document.getElementById('tc-'+n);
if(!card||card.classList.contains('flipped'))return;
card.classList.add('flipped');
flipped[n-1]=true;
if(flipped[0]&&flipped[1]&&flipped[2]){
setTimeout(function(){var c=document.getElementById('tarot-continue');if(c)c.style.display='';},900);
}
};
})();
</script>

:: Shana's Verdict [venue-trishas] {"position":"900,1850","size":"100,100"}
<div class="trishas-frame">
<span class="trishas-strip">· · · · · · · · · ·</span>

'Nothing is particularly wrong with it,' she says, pushing it back towards you.

You hide it in your bag like an injured thing.

'Bring it back to me in six months' time.'

(set: $confidence to ($statGain: $confidence, 8))

(if: not ($haunts contains $haunt11))[
(set: $haunts to $haunts + (a: $haunt11))
<div class="haunt-box">
<div class="haunt-header">⟡ HAUNT COLLECTED ⟡</div>
<div class="haunt-name">THE SPREAD</div>
<div class="haunt-description">Accreted gathering's landfall; lipids in the engorged liver.</div>
<div class="haunt-work"><em>The work: Multiplicatio.</em></div>
