:: Lackland's Back Room [venue-lackland-back] {"position":"1200,1150","size":"100,100"}
(set: $awaitingLacklandPwd to false)\
Lackland's backroom. A game of table tennis.

Two men, play: Percy Ritson, bookseller and poet; in his thirties, looks like a lion rampant. Jack Curtis, poet, librettist and writer of thrillers. A grandee, silver tousled. It's match point.

