:: Rescue the page [dream pyre] {"position":"100,1850","size":"100,100"}
You pause, for a whole long minute, and think of yourself, so as to become, Trelawny, salvaging what he thought was Shelley's heart from the flaming corpse, and punch a fist into the flames to rescue the paper.

