'You write, too?' she says, oddly.

Tonight she's not working. So you leave, via the gents, because of which detour things sharpen.

As you go, you remember, wholly and as a lone, remarkable thought: Ronnie Scott's. You'd forgotten it was there.
(set: $knowsRonnies to true)
<span class="guided-link">[[You remember that Ronnie Scott's is open and close.|Approach Ronnie Scott's]]</span>
[[Back to Dean Street|Dean Street]]
