:: The Colony Room Door [outdoor] {"position":"1200,550","size":"100,100"}
(if: $visited is a datamap and $visited contains "Colony" and $visited's Colony is true)[(go-to: "The Colony Room")]\
(if: $metDavy is true)[(go-to: "The Colony Room")]\
(if: $metSalvu is true)[(go-to: "Colony Member")]\
You think you know where The Colony Room is. You're not a member, but a friend brought you there once before.

You find yourself with a choice of two doors.

On which do you knock?

[[Left|Maltese Gangsters]]
[[Right|The Colony Room]]

<script>if(window.coinGate)window.coinGate("Left","Right",true);</script>

:: Colony Member [outdoor] {"position":"1300,550","size":"100,100"}
Outside, leaning upon Dean Street, with a glass in his hand gone stray from another establishment, is the famous Davy Merkin.

'Are you looking for me?' he says. You know you can't get past the door alone. 'Come upstairs. We'll drink.'

(link: "Drink with Davy Merkin")[(set: $sobriety to ($statLoss: $sobriety, 9))(go-to: "Davy Merkin")]

