:: The Interval [interval-radio] {"position":"900,250","size":"100,100"}
(if: $visitedInterval is true)[(go-to: "Dean Street")]\
<span class="staircase-marker" style="display:none"></span>
(unless: $alba is an array)[(set: $alba to (a:))]
(unless: $haunts is an array)[(set: $haunts to (a:))]
(set: $visitedInterval to true)\
(set: $visitedCarthage to true)\
Salt on the lip. Cinder in the lashes. The pyre's heat lifts from your face the way a hand lifts from your face — and you wake.

A flight of stairs, the kind you find leaving a theatre; red carpet worn thin as your world in its dead middle. Brass banister under your hand, still warm from other hands. Somewhere, a radio is just barely playing; what it plays, you cannot say.

<div class="lily-window">
A woman passes; she is going up. Two steps down you freeze, stopped clock, right twice: you'd know that perfume anywhere. It's Lily.
(set: $confidence to ($statGain: $confidence, 12))\
(set: $sobriety to ($statGain: $sobriety, 10))\
She goes upstairs. You go down.
<span class="lily-thought">(link: "Turn and follow her")[<span class="lily-fade-in">You take the stairs by doubles but when you get there she's gone. Lily-of-the-Valley is all that remains on the spendthrift draught.</span>(if: $sawMemory3 is false)[(set: $sawMemory3 to true)(replace: ?lilyPolaroid)[<div class="memory-photo memory-photo-3"><div class="mp-image"><svg class="mp-bg" viewBox="0 0 300 200" preserveAspectRatio="xMidYMid slice"><defs><radialGradient id="fl3" cx="50%" cy="40%" r="88%"><stop offset="0%" stop-color="#f8c8a8" stop-opacity="1"/><stop offset="22%" stop-color="#e89878" stop-opacity="0.78"/><stop offset="52%" stop-color="#a05060" stop-opacity="0.32"/><stop offset="100%" stop-color="#1a0a18" stop-opacity="0"/></radialGradient></defs><rect width="300" height="200" fill="url(#fl3)"/></svg><div class="mp-prose">In a certain memory she sits on your bed, dressing; she is in her underwear, which is black and laced. Since then, and before it, life has rarely been so real. You'd burn Troy after Troy to see God's face like that again.</div></div></div>]]

<span class="alba-link-fade">[[Down again.|Dean Street]]</span>]</span>
</div>

|lilyPolaroid>[]

