ass="nb-napkin-caption">Returned to O&#39;Flatterly.</div></div>')](else-if: $hasMissingPage is true)[(set: _nb to _nb + '<div class="nb-inv-item"><div class="nb-inv-name nb-item">◈ Page 93</div><div class="nb-inv-graphic-wrap"><svg class="nb-inv-page" viewBox="0 0 80 110" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><defs><linearGradient id="pgPaper" x1="0" y1="0" x2="0" y2="1"><stop offset="0%" stop-color="#f4e9ce"/><stop offset="100%" stop-color="#e0d3b0"/></linearGradient></defs><ellipse cx="40" cy="103" rx="26" ry="2" fill="rgba(0,0,0,0.22)"/><g transform="rotate(2 40 55)"><path d="M 14 8 L 17 12 L 13 18 L 16 24 L 14 30 L 17 36 L 15 44 L 16 52 L 14 60 L 17 68 L 14 76 L 16 84 L 14 92 L 17 98 L 68 98 L 68 8 Z" fill="url(#pgPaper)" stroke="rgba(130,95,55,0.55)" stroke-width="0.6"/><line x1="22" y1="20" x2="62" y2="20" stroke="rgba(60,38,12,0.6)" stroke-width="0.5"/><line x1="22" y1="26" x2="60" y2="26" stroke="rgba(60,38,12,0.5)" stroke-width="0.5"/><line x1="22" y1="32" x2="62" y2="32" stroke="rgba(60,38,12,0.55)" stroke-width="0.5"/><line x1="22" y1="38" x2="56" y2="38" stroke="rgba(60,38,12,0.5)" stroke-width="0.5"/><line x1="22" y1="44" x2="61" y2="44" stroke="rgba(60,38,12,0.55)" stroke-width="0.5"/><line x1="22" y1="50" x2="58" y2="50" stroke="rgba(60,38,12,0.45)" stroke-width="0.5"/><line x1="22" y1="56" x2="62" y2="56" stroke="rgba(60,38,12,0.55)" stroke-width="0.5"/><line x1="22" y1="62" x2="55" y2="62" stroke="rgba(60,38,12,0.45)" stroke-width="0.5"/><line x1="22" y1="68" x2="60" y2="68" stroke="rgba(60,38,12,0.55)" stroke-width="0.5"/><line x1="22" y1="74" x2="48" y2="74" stroke="rgba(60,38,12,0.42)" stroke-width="0.5"/><text x="40" y="91" text-anchor="middle" fill="rgba(50,28,8,0.95)" font-family="Playfair Display, Georgia, serif" font-size="9" font-style="italic" font-weight="600">93</text><ellipse cx="56" cy="78" rx="3" ry="2" fill="rgba(140,90,40,0.18)"/><circle cx="60" cy="82" r="1.4" fill="rgba(140,90,40,0.14)"/><circle cx="24" cy="86" r="1.8" fill="rgba(140,90,40,0.14)"/></g></svg></div><div class="nb-napkin-caption">For O&#39;Flatterly.</div></div>')](else:)[(set: _nb to _nb + '<div class="nb-inv-item nb-inv-locked"><div class="nb-grey">○ A missing page</div></div>')]\
